<section class='events'>
  <h2>The Event</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="column column--events">
      <h3>Hackathon</h3>
      <h4>Create something cool in a team of up to four.</h4>
      <p>This is where participants can build any software and hardware project of their choice. At the end, each team will be given the chance to showcase their project to other particpants and judges for a chance to win one or more of the top prizes. There will be mentors and volunteers to assist you at every step of the way.</p>
        <p>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="column column--events">
      <h3>Learnathon</h3>
      <h4>Join us and learn about technology.</h4>
      <p>Participate in workshops with like-minded peers to learn about software and hardware programming in a fun casual atmosphere. Get the opportunity to talk to leaders from the industry, and upper-year university students currently completing math and engineering degrees.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h4 class="column--footer">And don't worry about food and drinks—it's on us.</h4>
